{"tid":1545664,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"罷食吉野家！","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:14:54.000Z","uid":147376,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25e2d3f6bbd178f7658a7ef7958763fd4109a2a7","tid":1545664,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人唔可以再善忘，杯葛出賣港人嘅奶共企業！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/删-獅子狗-廣告-吉野家香港經營公司-極之憤怒-解僱廣告事務員工/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%88%A0-%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E7%8B%97-%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E5%90%89%E9%87%8E%E5%AE%B6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%93%E7%87%9F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E6%A5%B5%E4%B9%8B%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92-%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=3241a01b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%88%A0-%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E7%8B%97-%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E5%90%89%E9%87%8E%E5%AE%B6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%93%E7%87%9F%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E6%A5%B5%E4%B9%8B%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92-%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%2F&h=ad78fc2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/删-獅子狗-廣告-吉野家香港經營公司-極之憤怒-解僱廣告事務員工/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">吉野家早前在&nbsp;facebook 「獅子狗」宣傳，似是呼應網民以諧音諷刺日前在大埔連儂牆撕走警員資料的防暴警是「撕紙狗」，惟昨日已删去有關廣告。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">擁有吉野家香港經營權的香港合興集團有限公司，其總裁、全國政協委員洪明基接受《大公報》及《文匯報》訪問時指，對事件後表示極為憤怒，已和涉事的外判廣告公司解約，並解僱負責廣告事務的公司員工。</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>洪明基表示，自己近期剛剛參加了撐警大會，全力支持特區政府依法施政</strong></span>，就發生有關事件非常痛心，目前該廣告已經刪除。<br />\n他提到，涉事的外判廣告公司已經解約，負責廣告事務的公司員工已被解聘。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1f092efd483d84071335d0a27a4966e4452374fc","tid":1545664,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:59:46.000Z"